116
00:11:23,132 --> 00:11:24,394
Espera um minuto.

117
00:11:30,906 --> 00:11:32,339
Aqui.

118
00:11:33,142 --> 00:11:34,700
Toma isso.

119
00:11:42,985 --> 00:11:44,282
Cabe.

120
00:12:14,183 --> 00:12:15,616
E aí, pai.

121
00:12:48,984 --> 00:12:51,452
